aims of the project?

183
00:09:18.525 --> 00:09:21.120
Are you really
evaluating the aims?

184
00:09:21.120 --> 00:09:23.370
Have you got good coverage?

185
00:09:23.370 --> 00:09:26.490
Are you assessing,

186
00:09:26.490 --> 00:09:28.965
