188
00:09:31.440 --> 00:09:34.440
Are the results of your
evaluation well presented?

189
00:09:34.440 --> 00:09:35.610
Are they easy to understand?

190
00:09:35.610 --> 00:09:38.610
Can the person reading
it understand both what

191
00:09:38.610 --> 00:09:40.260
the results are and also how

192
00:09:40.260 --> 00:09:42.030
