on those results?

196
00:09:50.730 --> 00:09:52.680
Are you really thinking
about those benefits?

197
00:09:52.680 --> 00:09:54.705
This is what I was
talking about just now.

198
00:09:54.705 --> 00:09:58.710
What have you learned? What's
new about the project?

199
00:09:58.710 --> 00:10:00.090
What has not succeeded so well,

200
00:10:00.090 --> 00:10:01.950
and what have you
realized that's different

201
00:10:01.950 --> 00:10:04.335
from your original aims?

202
00:10:04.335 --> 00:10:09.375
Importantly, this is
using the results.

203
00:10:09.375 --> 00:10:14.300
This would be very much
grounded in any data,

204
00:10:14.300 --> 00:10:15.965
any user evaluation or

205
00:10:15.965 --> 00:10:19.140
any driven evaluation
that you have.

206
00:10:20.950 --> 00:10:24.275
The little crowning
glory will be,

207
00:10:24.275 --> 00:10:27.245
