evidence of originality.

208
00:10:27.245 --> 00:10:30.620
Again, as I said last
time, you don't need to.

209
00:10:30.620 --> 00:10:33.290
If you get zero for this,
that's absolutely fine.

210
00:10:33.290 --> 00:10:34.640
Most projects get zero for this.

211
00:10:34.640 --> 00:10:38.120
But it is there

212
00:10:38.120 --> 00:10:39.290
for people who want to push

213
00:10:39.290 --> 00:10:41.400
themselves a little bit harder.

214
00:10:42.460 --> 00:10:44.630
In a sense, the last
thing we're going

215
00:10:44.630 --> 00:10:46.490
